	* include/asio/detail/service_registry.hpp: Fix crash in comparison
	  of service ids.

2007-02-13 18:13  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/detail/posix_fd_set_adapter.hpp: Solaris defines
	  FD_ZERO to use an unqualified call to memset, so we need to make
	  the function visible using 'using namespace std'.

2007-02-09 16:47  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/: basic_socket_acceptor.hpp,
	  socket_acceptor_service.hpp: Add is_open() function to acceptor.

2007-02-09 12:59  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/detail/socket_ops.hpp: Fix to correctly clear error
	  after successful call of WSAAddresstoString or
	  WSAStringToAddress.

2007-02-09 11:59  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/detail/: hash_map.hpp, socket_types.hpp: Fix use of
	  hash_value overloads to work on x64 with the Vista version of the
	  Platform SDK.

2007-02-07 09:33  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/detail/old_win_sdk_compat.hpp: Use IN6ADDR_ANY_INIT
	  rather than IPPROTO_IPV6 to detect whether the Windows Platform
	  SDK supports IPv6, since the Vista Platform SDK has changed
	  IPPROTO_IPV6 to an enum.

