	  needed to fix multiple definition errors.

2006-11-17 22:34  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/detail/win_iocp_io_service.hpp: Add a workaround for
	  an apparent Windows bug where the delivery of asynchronous I/O
	  completions is delayed if the thread used to start the operation
	  is CPU bound.

