	  success.

2006-11-16 22:23  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/detail/strand_service.hpp: Remove unnecessary invoke
	  hook since the default one provides the correct behaviour, and
	  including it here for the invoke_current_handler class breaks
	  MSVC 7.1 when generating browse information.

