	  header.

2006-11-09 13:14  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/ssl/detail/openssl_init.hpp: The
	  openssl_locking_func() callback can be invoked through
	  OpenSSL_add_ssl_algorithms(), which causes instance() to be
	  called recursively before the static shared_ptr was initialized.

