2006-08-10 00:36  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/detail/win_iocp_socket_service.hpp: Implement socket
	  operation cancellation on Win32. The cancel call only works if
	  all operations for the socket have been issued from the same
	  thread, otherwise it fails with asio::error::not_supported.

