2006-04-05 23:32  chris_kohlhoff

	* src/doc/: index.html.in, boost/index.html: Add QNX to list of
	  supported platforms.

2006-04-05 22:46  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/: basic_io_service.hpp, error.hpp,
	  system_exception.hpp, detail/socket_ops.hpp: Add support for QNX.

2006-04-05 07:57  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/detail/hash_map.hpp: Clear the list before resetting
	  the buckets' iterator values to work around an STLPort checked
	  iterator warning.

2006-03-30 00:00  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/buffer.hpp: Remove incorrect buffer() overloads for
	  std::vector<const Pod_Type>.

2006-03-22 16:46  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/: basic_io_service.hpp, detail/socket_ops.hpp: Don't
	  globally block SIGPIPE if an alternative is available. On Linux,
	  the MSG_NOSIGNAL flag is now passed to the sendmsg function. On
	  Mac OS X, the SOL_SOCKET/SO_NOSIGPIPE socket option is set on all
	  sockets.

2006-03-22 16:00  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/detail/: reactive_socket_service.hpp,
	  socket_ops.hpp, socket_select_interrupter.hpp: Use sendmsg and
	  readmsg for all socket send and receive operations on non-Windows
	  platforms.

2006-03-06 11:59  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/basic_socket.hpp: Add missing return keyword.

2006-03-02 12:11  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/detail/select_reactor.hpp: Need to add 1 to the
	  maximum descriptor value passed to select(). Somehow this was
	  lost when a previous change was reverted.

2006-02-27 10:44  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/detail/task_io_service.hpp: The task_cleanup nested
	  class needs to be a friend of handler_base.

2006-02-27 09:27  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/detail/: task_io_service.hpp,
	  win_iocp_io_service.hpp: Don't use classes nested in function
	  definitions since they cause problems for the VC7.1 linker.

2006-02-27 08:11  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/ip/address.hpp: Try converting string to IPv6
	  address first to get a better error message if it's an invalid
	  string and IPv6 is not supported on the system.

