2005-11-13 22:32  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/error.hpp: Make cleanup of buffer allocated by
	  FormatMessage exception-safe. Use FormatMessageA instead of
	  FormatMessage since we're always using a narrow character string.
	  Use a string literal instead of character literal in output to
	  work around BCB bug. Thanks to Pavel Vozenilek for suggesting
	  these changes.

