	  src/tests/unit/ipv4/host_resolver_test.cpp: Rename the Stream
	  concept's read and write to read_some and write_some to make it
	  clear that those functions may result in only a partial transfer
	  of data. Combine read_n and read_at_least_n into a single read
	  function (and the equivalent for write). Add a new error_type
	  typedef on most types so that generic code can construct the
	  appropriate object.

