	  check for correct RTL into push_options.hpp and add support for
	  MSVC.

2005-08-12 00:04  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/detail/socket_types.hpp: Prevent inclusion of
	  wspiapi.h when building with Borland C++, as it breaks
	  precompiled headers. Add define for WIN32_LEAN_AND_MEAN to speed
	  up compilation. Thanks to Pavel Vozenilek for these suggestions.

2005-08-12 00:03  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/detail/win_thread.hpp: Check that the correct RTL is
	  being used when compiling with Borland C++.  Thanks to Pavel
	  Vozenilek for this suggestion.

