2004-11-24 16:57  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/detail/win_iocp_demuxer_service.hpp: Don't use
	  DWORD_PTR when building for target Windows versions earlier than
	  Windows 2000. This should allow asio to build using MSVC 6 with
	  the version of the Platform SDK that shipped with it. Thanks to
	  Zhuo Qiang for reporting this problem and suggesting a solution.

2004-11-24 16:43  chris_kohlhoff

	* include/asio/: arg.hpp, error_handler.hpp: Fixes to eliminate
	  multiply-defined symbol linker errors with MSVC 7.1.

2004-11-21 11:42  chris_kohlhoff

	* INSTALL, configure.ac, src/Makefile.bor, src/Makefile.mgw,
	  src/Makefile.msc: Updated build files to support boost 1.32.0.

