2004-11-19 09:19  chris_kohlhoff

	* THANKS, include/asio/detail/hash_map.hpp,
	  include/asio/detail/reactive_socket_connector_service.hpp,
	  include/asio/detail/reactor_op_queue.hpp,
	  include/asio/detail/select_reactor.hpp: Correctly check for
	  failures in non-blocking connection operations. This should fix
	  bug 1069007, where an async connection operation that was
	  expected to fail would never complete. Thanks to Zhuo Qiang for
	  reporting this problem.

2004-10-14 06:32  chris

	* INSTALL, README, configure.ac: asio version 0.1.13 released

2004-10-14 06:30  chris

	* src/Makefile.msc: Change MSVC makefile to support the free VC
	  toolkit out of the box. Thanks to Vladimir Slepnev <slepnev_v at
	  rambler dot ru> for suggesting this.

2004-09-23 22:16  chris

	* include/asio/ipv4/: address.hpp, tcp.hpp, udp.hpp: Fix network vs
	  host byte ordering issues when handling IPv4 addresses.

2004-09-23 17:48  chris

	* src/doc/Makefile.am: Rolled back the changes to the documentation
	  generation with respect to a separate build directory until the
	  appropriate behaviour is determined.

2004-09-23 00:42  chris

	* src/doc/Makefile.am: Generated docs should depend on asio.dox.in,
	  not asio.dox, so that the documentation is not recreated when
	  doing a build in a package.

2004-09-23 00:27  chris

	* include/asio/detail/reactor_timer_queue.hpp: Fix signed/unsigned
	  warning.

2004-09-23 00:17  chris

	* include/asio/detail/reactor_timer_queue.hpp: Fix for the case of
	  removing a timer from the end of the heap.

2004-09-22 23:13  chris

	* configure.ac, configure.in, src/doc/release_checklist.htm: Rename
	  configure.in to configure.ac to conform with newer practice.

2004-09-22 23:04  chris

	* Makefile.am, autogen.sh, include/Makefile.am, src/Makefile.am,
	  src/doc/Makefile.am, src/doc/asio.dox.in,
	  src/doc/release_checklist.htm: Improvements to better support
	  building in an alternative object directory.	Thanks to Carlo
	  Wood for providing these changes.

2004-09-22 22:58  chris

	* THANKS: Add Matthew Nourse and Carlo Wood.

2004-09-22 22:41  chris

	* configure.in: Update to support later versions of the autoconf
	  and automake tools.

2004-09-22 22:20  chris

	* include/asio/detail/reactor_timer_queue.hpp: Fix errors in the
	  calculation of the parent index of a heap element. Also fix
	  problem where we were comparing pointers instead of the time
	  values.

2004-09-22 22:17  chris

	* include/asio/detail/win_time.hpp: 64-bit integer constants need
	  an "LL" suffix when compiling with g++.  Thanks to Carlo Wood for
	  reporting this.

