2004-07-21 18:07  chris

	* include/asio/error.hpp: Only use Win32 error codes on Windows,
	  not errno values.

2004-07-21 17:07  chris

	* include/asio/detail/win_mutex.hpp: Windows critical sections use
	  structured exception handling to report errors, so wrap the
	  appropriate Windows API calls in __try/__except blocks.

2004-07-21 16:46  chris

	* configure.in, src/Makefile.mgw: The -mthreads option is required
	  for thread-safe exception handling with MinGW.

