	  examples/tutorial/daytime6/.cvsignore,
	  examples/tutorial/daytime6/server.cpp: Added UDP daytime tutorial
	  programs.

2004-04-23 17:33  chris

	* include/asio/detail/win_time.hpp: Add a static cast to prevent a
	  performance warning on MSVC 7.1

2004-04-23 16:39  chris

	* include/asio/detail/hash_map.hpp: Use an unsigned integer for the
	  hash value to prevent the possibility of trying to use a negative
	  bucket index.

2004-04-22 16:47  chris

	* src/Makefile.am: Added locking_dispatcher_test to list of unit
	  tests to be run when you do a `make check'.

2004-04-22 16:36  chris

	* INSTALL: Indicate that the Linux instructions also apply to UNIX.

2004-04-22 16:13  chris

	* src/doc/: asio.css, asio_footer.htm, asio_header.htm: Cosmetic
	  changes to generated documentation

2004-04-22 11:38  chris

	* INSTALL: Add note that gcc 3.4.0 has been tested.

2004-04-21 18:48  chris

	* src/examples/timeouts/: accept_timeout.cpp, connect_timeout.cpp,
	  dgram_recv_timeout.cpp: Remove unnecessary intermediate
	  handle_timeout function.

2004-04-21 17:31  chris

	* src/examples/tutorial/daytime3/server.cpp: Comment out the unused
	  function arguments to prevent a compiler warning.

2004-04-21 17:30  chris

	* include/: Makefile.am, asio/detail/hash_map.hpp,
	  asio/detail/reactive_timer_service.hpp,
	  asio/detail/reactor_op_queue.hpp,
	  asio/detail/reactor_timer_queue.hpp,
	  asio/detail/select_reactor.hpp: Add a new hash_map class which
	  replaces the map used by the reactor_op_queue. Change the timer
	  queue implementation to use the hash_map internally to map a
	  caller-supplied token to the waiting timers. This should fix the
	  race condition we had previously when setting the token to 0 in
	  the handler callback.

2004-04-16 12:53  chris

	* src/: doc/Makefile.am, doc/asio.dox.in, doc/asio_header.htm,
	  examples/tutorial/index_dox.txt, examples/tutorial/timer_dox.txt,
	  examples/tutorial/tutorial_dox.txt: Rearranged tutorial
	  documentation to make it easier to add new sections to the
	  tutorials.

2004-04-15 17:29  chris

	* src/examples/echo/blocking_tcp_echo_server.cpp: Use the thread
	  class from the asio namespace.

2004-04-15 17:29  chris

	* include/asio/thread.hpp: Clarify the behaviour of the thread
	  class when you fail to call join() before the thread object is
	  destroyed.

