	  callbacks if setting a timer causes it to expire.

2004-04-12 12:25  chris

	* include/Makefile.am, include/asio.hpp, include/asio/arg.hpp,
	  src/examples/chat/chat_client.cpp,
	  src/examples/chat/chat_server.cpp,
	  src/examples/echo/async_tcp_echo_server.cpp,
