	  src/tests/performance/server.cpp,
	  src/tests/unit/dgram_socket_test.cpp: Add support for named
	  placeholders in the callback arguments.

2004-04-11 11:37  chris

	* include/asio/buffered_send_stream.hpp, include/asio/recv.hpp,
	  include/asio/send.hpp, src/examples/chat/chat_client.cpp,
	  src/examples/chat/chat_server.cpp,
	  src/examples/echo/async_tcp_echo_server.cpp,
	  src/tests/performance/client.cpp,
	  src/tests/performance/server.cpp: Reversed the order of the
	  last_length and total_length parameters to the handler functions
	  for async_recv_n and async_send_n. Since users of these functions
	  are more likely to want to ignore the total_length parameter,
	  making it last allows it to be omitted from user-defined
	  handlers. This is because a functor created using boost::bind
	  will automatically discard excess arguments before invoking the
	  handler contained within it.

2004-04-11 11:13  chris

	* include/asio/socket_error.hpp: Undefine the ASIO_SOCKET_ERROR
	  macro when it is no longer needed.

2004-04-08 18:18  chris

	* src/: Makefile.am, Makefile.bor, Makefile.mgw, Makefile.msc,
	  examples/tutorial/daytime1/client.cpp,
	  examples/tutorial/daytime2/server.cpp: Start adding new tutorial
	  programs based around the daytime protocol.

