	  0.1.7 released

2004-04-06 17:29  chris

	* include/asio/detail/: reactive_dgram_socket_service.hpp,
	  reactive_socket_acceptor_service.hpp,
	  reactive_socket_connector_service.hpp,
	  reactive_stream_socket_service.hpp: Check if a socket is valid
	  before starting a new asynchronous operation. If it is not valid
	  then an error will be posted.

