	  original (i.e. they represent the same completion context).

2003-12-30 11:43  chris

	* include/asio/detail/: win_iocp_demuxer_service.hpp,
	  win_iocp_dgram_socket_service.hpp,
	  win_iocp_stream_socket_service.hpp: Ensure contexts get released
	  after the upcall is complete.

